flowchart TD
    Client([Client Request])
    Gateway[API Gateway]
    Auth{Authenticated?}
    RateLimit{Rate Limited?}
    Router[Service Router]

    UserSvc[User Service]
    OrderSvc[Order Service]
    NotifySvc[Notification Service]

    UserDB[(User DB\nPostgres)]
    OrderDB[(Order DB\nPostgres)]
    Cache[(Redis Cache)]
    Queue([Message Queue\nRabbitMQ])

    Client --> Gateway
    Gateway --> Auth
    Auth -->|No| Reject([401 Unauthorized])
    Auth -->|Yes| RateLimit
    RateLimit -->|Exceeded| TooMany([429 Too Many Requests])
    RateLimit -->|OK| Router

    Router --> UserSvc
    Router --> OrderSvc

    UserSvc --> UserDB
    UserSvc --> Cache
    OrderSvc --> OrderDB
    OrderSvc --> Queue
    Queue --> NotifySvc
    NotifySvc --> UserSvc

    style Client fill:#6c63ff,color:#fff
    style Gateway fill:#333,color:#fff
    style Reject fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff
    style TooMany fill:#e67e22,color:#fff
